      "message": "I\u0027m not sure if I understand this question correctly.\n\nIn your current implementation, similar to tree client, I think the clientCtxKey should map to an implementation of (interface) bq.Client. A struct with a bigquery.Client (i.e. the `Inserter` in your code) is a bq.Client implementation which is ideal to use in Prod. `MockClient` is the implementation that is used in test.",
